text: Missoula Hempfest is an annual cannabis event held in Missoula, Montana, in the United States. The fifth and tenth festivals were held in Caras Park in 2000 and 2005, respectively. ==See also== * Cannabis in Montana * Code of the West (2012 film) ==References== Category:1990s establishments in Montana Category:Cannabis events in the United States Category:Cannabis in Montana Category:Culture of Missoula, Montana Category:Festivals in Montana
